<div class="nbunit" id="15Oct1935"><font color="red">15 October 1935</font> <i>JJQ</i> (to James Stephens): I think I ought to give you the name of the best specialist in this line in the U.S. He is Dr Louis Berman, author of &lsquo;Glands Regulating Human Personality&rsquo; </div>
